title: The Monster is Ready for Dinner
alternative_titles: The Demon Is Ready For Dinner!
The Monster Is Ready for Dinner!
summary: The Monster is Ready for Dinner Manhua Yu Ni, a man with a few screws loose, bought a husky and embarked on a journey of killing monsters in mainland China, in order to find and retrieve his own perception and abilities. The talented great chef, beautiful young lady, Wuzai incidentally tasted monster’s meat and was greatly amazed at it afterward. She was determined to create a cookbook heirloom based on monsters. Then, the group went on the incredible killing monsters and making culinary adventures together! The Demon Is Ready For Dinner! The Monster Is Ready for Dinner! Yao Kaifan La! 妖开饭啦！
